          <p>Collably is my 'capstone' project. The Goal of collably was for me to conceive of an idea, organize the architecture, construct user stories, and complete the first iteration completely self-directed.</p>
          <p>I worked with a mentor of mine, Richard, in a Project Manager - Developer relationship. The purpose was for us to simulate a workplace development environment, while stretching my ability to solve problems.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              join tables, has_many :through, and added ActiveRecord complexity
            </li>
            <li>
              custom controller actions and instance methods for added functionality
            </li>
            <li>
              N + 1 database queries
            </li>
            <li>
              test-driven-development and agile development methodology
            </li>
            <li>
              implemented inbox system and message-board type communication
            </li>
            </br>
            <%# image_tag %>
            <a href= "https://github.com/yakschuss/collably" >Source Code</a>
            <div class="portfolio-box-caption">
          </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
